data.description: Beautiful single-story located on a spacious corner lot. Approximately 2150 square foot home featuring 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a study/office and a 2-car garage with an expanded driveway addition added to both sides of the driveway for extra room and convenience.  The rooms all have ceiling fans including the living room and master bedroom closet.  The open kitchen includes granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and open concept floorplan that opens to the dining area and family room. The Bedroom 1 suite is located off the family room and it includes a large walk-in closet and a relaxing spa-like bathroom.  The home is wired for a security system that can be set up with the company of your choice.  The back yard has an extended concrete patio with a free standing pergola that makes for a nice area to create your own back yard kitchen oasis.  Additional brick laid patio area off the pergola for added outdoor space.  Irrigation system in the front and back yard for the ease of maintaining a nice yard and foundation support.
